{
  "stem": "7860.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I chased them off with a little bayonet I had because I was playing in the field tending cows.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I scared them off like.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I went to the railroad station in Otwock, going to be taking the train going back to the peasant who I was staying with.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I fell asleep on a bench to be awakened at 12 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Train just arrived from the nearby villages in the direction where I was tending the cow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there were many people sitting at the [INAUDIBLE]-- black marketeers, Gentile black marketeers. heading to the direction for Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Later to have discovered-- so they used to disembark on the train in Otwock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So this is where they'd go with the train directly to Warsaw with the goodies they did business with.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The gendarmes would liquidate all the stuff they had. 4 o'clock train, electric train, would come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And there was [INAUDIBLE]-- it used to stop at every station before Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So to beat out the Germans from taking away their goods, they used to sleep it from 12 o'clock to 4 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I discovered a way to do so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There was a bookcase.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "In the daytime, it was a newspaper stand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And behind the bookcase was, like a-- was like a counter, also in front of the bookcase.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And behind the bookcase was a radiator on tall legs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "When a bookcase used to be closed-- this newspaper stand used to be closed-- I crawled behind the bookcase and underneath the radiator on a marble floor, I used to sleep there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I improvised a way of coming and going every night time to come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was no longer-- no ghetto, no more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I mentioned before, children would go around begging.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
